<title>Manipulating Matrices</title> 

	<objectives>
		<introduction>
			<p>
				By the end of this section, you will be able to ...
			</p>
		</introduction>
		<ol>
			<li>Compute the transpose of a matrix,</li>
			<li>Convert a matrix into a vector.</li>
